ive API，具有实时音频、视频流输入以及使用多个组合工具的能力。 明年初，Gemini 2.0 还会扩展到更多 Google 产品中。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-940d9e614caf30744f89e56a7ba6c00a_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "5.5 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/6633411738"}}, "attached_info": "CkEIq56egcOW84sDEAMaCTExMjMwMzI5NyCUzui6BjAAOO8BQBxyCjY2MzM0MTE3Mzh4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "29_1734051334.240328", "card_id": "Q_273748436", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 87}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "《拯救大兵瑞恩》开头的抢滩登陆真的符合军事学吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "如题，《拯救大兵瑞恩》开头的登陆战已经成为二战电影的经典片段，看过两遍被震撼的同时也一直在想：这种由登陆艇直接把士兵往海滩上送，明知开了隔板就是机枪火力压制的登陆作战真的合理吗？个人感觉如果有炮火掩护，或者由空军在海岸线投下烟雾弹也可以提供掩护吧。 以上只是个人看法，如果讲的不对请多包涵，欢迎指正。希望各位可以分享一下看法，多谢多谢！ 再多问一句吧，如果在现代战争中打这么一场登陆战该如何去打？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-eb558d979d921c09bb843de05733226a_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "5.5 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/273748436"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Iq56egcOW84sDEAMaCDIzMTA4MjIwILSs29YFMAA4lwJAHXIJMjczNzQ4NDM2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}], "paging": {"is_end": true, "is_start": false, "next": "", "previous": "", "totals": 0}, "fresh_text": "热榜已更新", "display_num": 15, "display_first": true, "fb_bill_main_rise": 0, "head_zone": {"type": "billboard_lantern", "data": [{"id": "1724871100431802368", "link_url": "https://www.zhihu.com/appview/community_construction", "title": "辟谣专区", "source_type": 0, "attached_info": "Ci4QABoTMTcyNDg3MTEwMDQzMTgwMjM2OHITMTcyNDg3MTEwMDQzMTgwMjM2OHgA", "tag": "辟谣", "tag_bg_color": "GRD01A"}, {"id": "1850641407875878912", "link_url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/6589259992", "title": "